eeb a lot,'' the mother said, adding that the siblings were close friends. `` I could n't believe it when they were in there arguing the other day. It was great.'' <PERSON> Missy </PERSON>'s struggle is far from over. The left side of her body remains paralyzed. <PERSON> Goebel </PERSON> said his daughter often slips into a `` kind of dream state'' and gets confused easily. `` She's pretty much like a rag doll,'' he said. `` But she's further along than anyone ever thought she would be.
